Covariate analysis for the population PK model was restricted to the relationship between the different categorizations of ADA status (ADAEVER, ADAONE, ADALOCF, etc.) and avelumab CL. The ADA-CL relationship was implemented using a linear function:\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
